node.text:
This has truly been a labor of love! “DWYANE” my photographic memoir with a genuine, behind-the-scenes look at my life on and off the court is officially available for presale! Link in bio 💯📖

A huge THANK YOU to my brother @justintinsley for creating such a dope structure for this book and for bringing my words to life. My brother @bobbymetelus and I, were connected at the hip during some special times in my life and we’re excited to share some of those moments with you all.
